{"body": "@fxn \r\n\r\nThere is a great argument to be had that my pull's ugliness, using `!!(whatever)` isn't worth it. I understand that.\r\n\r\nYou, and the other rails-core guys, are leaders in our field and owners of a fantastic web framework, many including myself would say it's the best web framework. Part of being a great leader is realizing when you're wrong. It's natural to be defensive and it's fine to argue every counterpoint. And you're right about many of them. But the strength of your argument is not stronger than the collective opinion of this community.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/4671621", "created_at": "2012-03-24T04:46:18Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/5329#issuecomment-4671621", "updated_at": "2012-03-24T04:46:18Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 5329, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/clifton/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/clifton/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/clifton/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/clifton", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/clifton/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/clifton", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/clifton/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/4cede21ea96795d2de831e9981cc81cd?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fc27181a18d3b30d14d66a1a56c068548.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/clifton/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/clifton/received_events", "gravatar_id": "4cede21ea96795d2de831e9981cc81cd", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/clifton/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "clifton", "type": "User", "id": 14217, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/clifton/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523819bdbd3543c15100e249"}, "id": 4671621, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/5329"}
